---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Terms of Service | Pejji" description="Terms and conditions for Pejji's web design and development services.">

  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold reveal">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-subtle text-sm reveal" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">Last updated: 30 March 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-10 text-subtle leading-relaxed reveal" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-light mb-3">Service Description</h2>
          <p>Pejji provides professional web design and development services for Nigerian businesses. We build custom, mobile-first websites tailored to your business needs.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-light mb-3">Pricing</h2>
          <p>Our pricing is as listed on our <a href="/services" class="text-teal hover:underline">Services &amp; Pricing</a> page. Prices are subject to change, but any agreed price at the time of deposit is honoured for that project.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-light mb-3">Payment Terms</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>A 50% deposit is required before we begin building your website</li>
            <li>The remaining balance is due before your site goes live</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-light mb-3">Revision Policy</h2>
          <p>The number of revision rounds included depends on your service tier:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li><strong class="text-light">Card</strong> — 1 round of revisions</li>
            <li><strong class="text-light">Starter</strong> — 2 rounds of revisions</li>
            <li><strong class="text-light">Growth &amp; Pro</strong> — 3 rounds of revisions</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">Additional revisions beyond the included rounds may incur extra charges.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-light mb-3">Hosting</h2>
          <p>Hosting is provided on a monthly subscription basis. If you wish to cancel your hosting, we require 30 days' written notice. Upon cancellation, your website files can be transferred to you upon request.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-light mb-3">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>You retain full ownership of all content you provide (text, images, logos, brand assets)</li>
            <li>Pejji retains rights to the underlying code, design templates, and development frameworks</li>
            <li>All websites include a "Built by Pejji" badge as part of the service agreement</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-light mb-3">Referral Programme</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>Referral commissions are paid within 7 business days of receiving the referred client's deposit</li>
            <li>Pejji reserves the right to modify commission rates with reasonable notice</li>
            <li>Full referral programme details are available on our <a href="/partners" class="text-teal hover:underline">Partners</a> page</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-light mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>Pejji shall not be held liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our services. Our total liability shall not exceed the amount paid by the client for the specific service in question.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-light mb-3">Governing Law</h2>
          <p>These terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the Federal Republic of Nigeria.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-light mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p>For questions about these terms, email us at <a href="mailto:hello@pejji.com" class="text-teal hover:underline">hello@pejji.com</a>.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
